      "chapter": "Kidan",
      "stanza": "Part2",
      "english": "፨ MORNING PRAYER OF THE COVENANT ፨\nPriest: The Grace of God be with you.\n፨ People: and with Your Spirit.",
      "geez_script": "ካህን፤ ጸጋ ዘእግዚአብሔር የሃሉ ምስሌክሙ።\n፨ ሕዝብ፤ ምስለ መንፈስከ።",
