      "english": "Priest: My fathers and my brothers pray for me and for this sacrifice.",
      "geez_script": "ካህን፤ ጸልዩ አበውየ ወአኀውየ ላዕሌየ ወላዕለ ዝንቱ መሥዋዕት።",
