      "geez_phonetic": "kahn: leke lezeyḳewmu ḳdméke 'ilf 'a'ilafat wet'ilfīte 'a'ilafat ḳdusan mela'ikt welīḳane mela'ikt wekburan 'inssake 'ile sidistutu knefīhomu surafél wekīrubél",
