      "amharic_phonetic": "kahn: 'a'ilafe 'a'ilafa tna t'ilfīte 'a'ilafat yemīhonu ḳdusan mela'i kt yemela'iktm 'ale ḳoch knfachew sdst yemīhon kburan 'arba 'itu 'inssam kefīth lemīḳomulh le'ante :",
