      "reference": "",
      "chapter": "Apostles",
      "stanza": "57",
      "english": "Deacon: Stand up for prayer.\n፨ People: Lord have mercy upon us.\nPriest: Peace be unto you all.\n፨ People: And with Your Spirit.",
      "geez_script": "ካህን፤ ተንሥኡ ለጸሎት\n፨ ሕዝብ፤ እግዚኦ ተሣሃለነ\nዲያቆን፤  ሰላም ለኵልክሙ\n፨ ሕዝብ፤ ምስለ መንፈስከ",
      "geez_phonetic": "kahn: tens'u letselot\n፨ ḥzb: 'igzī'o tesahalene\ndīyaḳon:  selam lekwlkmu\n፨ ḥzb: msle menfeske",
