      "chapter": "Apostles",
      "stanza": "58",
      "english": "Priest: And again we beseech the almighty God, the Father of our Lord and our Saviour Jesus Christ.",
      "geez_script": "ካህን፤ ወካዕበ ናስተበቍዕ ዘኵሎ ይእኅዝ እግዚአብሔር አብ ለእግዚእ ወመድኃኒነ ኢየሱስ ክርስቶስ፤",
      "geez_phonetic": "kahn: weka'ibe nastebeḳw'i zekwlo y'ihz 'igzī'abḥér 'ab le'igzī'i wemedhanīne 'īyesus krstos :",
