      "reference": "",
      "chapter": "Apostles",
      "stanza": "61",
      "english": "Priest: all in Christ, through whom to you with him and with the Holy Spirit be glory and dominion, both now and ever and world without end. Amen.",
      "geez_script": "ካህን፤ በክርስቶስ ዘቦቱ ለከ ምስሌሁ ወምስለ ቅዱስ መንፈስ ስብሐት ወእኂዝ ይእዜኒ ወዘ ልፈኒ ወለዓለመ ዓለም አሜን፤",
