      "chapter": "Apostles",
      "stanza": "65",
      "english": "፨ ALL: Let us draw near the face of the Saviour of the world ye ye ye. In the faith which is of him let us submit ourselves to Christ.",
      "geez_script": "፨ ኵሎሙ: ወንብጻሕ ቅድመ ገጹ ለመድኃኔ ዓለም ዬ ዬ ዬ በአሚነ ዚአሁ ለክርስቶስ ንገኒ፣",
