      "reference": "",
      "chapter": "Apostles",
      "stanza": "98",
      "english": "Priest: which is given for life and for salvation and for remission of sin unto them that receive of it in faith.\n፨ People: Amen.",
      "geez_script": "ካህን፤ ዘይትወሀብ ለሕይወት ወለመድኃኒት ወለሥርየተ ኀጢአት ለእለ ይነሥኡ እምኔሁ በአሚን \n፨ ሕዝብ፤ አሜን።",
