      "geez_phonetic": "akwetéte ḳwrban ze'igz'itne maryam dngl weladīte 'amlak 'amlak zederese bemenfes ḳdus 'aba ḥryaḳos 'ép̣īsḳop̣os zehagere bhnsa :",
