      "amharic_phonetic": "kahn: yebhnsa 'ép̣īsḳop̣os 'aba ḥryaḳos 'amlakn sle weledech sle 'imebétachn dngl maryam bemenfes ḳdus yederesew yeḳwīrban msgana yh new ,",
