      "geez_phonetic": "kahn: 'o ml'ite tsega 'o muḥaze fsha. fedfade bkī grma ra'iy zeye'abī 'imkīrubél 'ile bzuhat 'a'iyntīhomu wesurafél 'ile sdstu knefīhomu.",
