      "reference": "Theotokia",
      "chapter": "St.Mary",
      "stanza": "46",
      "english": "Priest: you did conceive Him without His being limited, and He stayed in your womb without making subtraction from above or addition beneath.",
      "geez_script": "ካህን፤ ሐለበ ሐሊበ እንዘ ውእቱ ዘይሴሲ ኵሎ።",
