      "english": "Priest: The Diety does not stoop or bow down the head to take up that which is on earth, but all is in His hand as He showed to Peter.",
      "geez_script": "ካህን፤ ኦ ድንግል መኑ ይትመሰለኪ። አንቲ ውእቱ ርእሰ ሕግ ወተፍጻሜተ ቃለ እግዚአብሔር።",
      "geez_phonetic": "kahn: 'o dngl menu ytmeslekī. 'antī w'itu r'ise ḥg weteftsaméte ḳale 'igzī'abḥér.",
