      "chapter": "St.Mary",
      "stanza": "54",
      "english": "Priest: We believe that the life-giving Holy Spirit is Holy Spirit in his nature. Three names but one God.",
      "geez_script": "ካህን፤ ዐንቀጸ ባሕር አንቲ ዘተሣየጠኪ በዐል ዓለም ኢየሱስ ክርስቶስ እምውሥጠ መዝገብ።",
