      "english": "፨ People: Ascended in glory into heaven, sat at the right hand of his Father, and will come again in glory to judge the living and the dead; there is no end of his reign.",
      "geez_script": "፨ ሕዝብ፤ ዐርገ በስብሐት ውስተ ሰማያት ወነበረ በየማነ አቡሁ ዳግመ ይመጽእ በስብሐት ይኰንን ሕያዋነ ወሙታነ ወአልቦ ምኅለቅት ለመንግሥቱ",
      "geez_phonetic": "፨ ḥzb: 'arge besbḥat wste semayat wenebere beyemane 'abuhu dagme ymets'i besbḥat ykwenn ḥyawane wemutane we'albo mhleḳt lemengstu",
