      "amharic_phonetic": "፨ ḥzb: bekbr wede semay 'arege: be'abatum ḳeñ teḳemeṭe. dagmeñam hyawanna mutann ygeza zend begétnet ymeṭal. lemengstum ftsamé yelewm:",
