      "chapter": "The300",
      "stanza": "8",
      "english": "፨ People: And we believe in the Holy Spirit, the life-giving GOD, who proceeds from the Father; we worship and glorify him with the Father and the Son; who spoke by the prophets.",
      "geez_script": "፨ ሕዝብ፤ ወነአምን በመንፈስ ቅዱስ እግዚእ ምኅየዊ ዘሠረፀ እምአብ ንስግድ ሎቱ ወንሰብሖ ምስለ አብ ወወልድ ዘነበበ በነቢያት",
