      "reference": "The Institution Narrative",
      "chapter": "St.Mary",
      "stanza": "99",
      "english": "Priest: and when there was counted with them Judas whose creation was like the tares added to wheat, and who betrayed Him.",
      "geez_script": "ካህን፤ ወእንዘ ይትኈለቍ ምስሌሆሙ ይሁዳ ዘፍጥረቱ ክርዳድ ዘተወሰከ ምስለ ስንዴ ዘአሕለፎ።",
