      "chapter": "St.Mary",
      "stanza": "103",
      "english": "Priest: He looked up to heaven towards You his Father, interceded with His parent, and committed His disciples to Him to keep them from from all evil:",
      "geez_script": "ካህን፤ ነጸረ ውስተ ሰማይ ኀበ አቡሁ አስተብቍዐ ኀበ ወላዲሁ ወአማኀዘኖሙ አርዳኢሁ ከመ ይዕቀቦሙ እምኵሉ እኩይ።",
      "geez_phonetic": "kahn: netsere wste semay habe 'abuhu 'astebḳw'a habe weladīhu we'amaḥezenomu 'arda'īhu keme y'iḳebomu 'imkwlu 'ikuy.",
