      "reference": "Prayer of the Angels",
      "chapter": "St.Mary",
      "stanza": "148",
      "english": "Priest: We lay our souls before You, Lord, Maker of all, the invisible God. We humble ourselves to You, the humbler of all. We worship You, who make all to worship Uou. We serve You, ruler of all.",
