      "stanza": "99",
      "english": "Priest: which is given for life and for salvation and for remission of sin unto those who drink of it in faith. \n፨ People:  Amen.",
      "geez_script": "ካህን፤ ዘይትወሀብ ለሕይወት ወለመድኃኒት ወለሥርየት ኃጢአት ለእለ ይትሜጠዉ እምኔሁ በአሚን\n፨ ሕዝብ፤ አሜን።",
      "geez_phonetic": "kahn: zeytwehab leḥywet welemedhanīt welesryet haṭī'at le'ile ytméṭewu 'imnéhu be'amīn\n፨ ḥzb: 'amén.",
