      "amharic_phonetic": "፨ ḥzb: : bemamen 'abat byé 'iṭerahalehu, mengsthnm 'iṭe ralehu, 'abétu smh beña lay ymesgen, msgun kbur yemt hon hayal 'ante nehna, le'ante kbr ygebahal lezele'alemu?",
