      "english": "Priest (to the faithful):  The Lord be with you all.\n፨ People: and with Your Spirit.",
      "geez_script": "ካህን፤... እግዚአብሔር የሃሉ ምስለ ኵልክሙ።\n፨ ሕዝብ፤ ምስለ መንፈስከ።",
